    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape. No scratches, no dings, and it drives like a total dream. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
