    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six engine delivering a linear power band and 385 hp. This specimen boasts a precise 6-speed manual transaxle paired with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis is sharpened by PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), maintaining optimal damping across all lateral load phases. Meticulously maintained with zero bore scoring concerns and a documented over-rev report showing only Range 1 ignitions. The Arctic Silver metallic finish retains its factory depth, while the interior displays zero bolster wear or switchgear delamination. A true purist\u2019s specification in turn-key, showroom condition.",
